import MainLayout from '../layouts/main.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Scene" page="Scene">
    <div class="e5_5"></div>
    <p>The police found some <a href="/CrimeSceneSite/evidence/">evidence</a> at the crime scene. Here they identified 3
        <a href="/CrimeSceneSite/suspects/">suspects</a>. Some witnesses were contacted and gave their statements:
    <ul>
        <li>
            <div>Eggvan Tanner (Someone else in the homeless shelter):</div>
            Joe Cau recently fell ill, and his friend and Arik Wong told me they were getting medicine for him
            When Arik returned, he was unwilling to disclose where he got his medicine from and what it was, so I
            assumed that it was something illegal, but snitches get stitches, y'know?
        </li>
        <li>
            <div>Brendan Goh-Away (Passer-by on the street):</div>
            In a nearby alleyway, I saw someone short, dressed in a red jacket, stooped over and talking to a man
            dressed in all black, when a suspicious exchange of something occurred
        </li>
        <li>
            <div>Daisy Meerollin:</div>
            Arik went out earlier today, and he wouldn't tell anyone where he was going
            Dwain Durug Jonken has been known to indulge in buying and selling drugs on occasion, but when I saw him
            earlier today, he appeared sober
        </li>
    </ul>
    </p>
</MainLayout>

<style>
    .e5_5 {
        box-shadow: 8px 8px 0px rgba(40.00000141561031, 37.00000159442425, 37.00000159442425, 1);
        background-image: url("/CrimeSceneSite/alignedscene.png");
        background-repeat: no-repeat;
        background-size: 100% 100%;
        background-color: aliceblue;
        width: min(20rem, 100%-8px);
        aspect-ratio: 4.5 / 3;
        height: 400px;
        border-top-left-radius: 47px;
        border-top-right-radius: 47px;
        border-bottom-left-radius: 47px;
        border-bottom-right-radius: 47px;
        border: 8px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 1);
    }
</style>